{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Kuroe","narration":"I lost consciousness...","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"...and as I continued to sink..."},{"narration":"I had a dream."},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"black","narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm24_story07","nameNarration":"","narration":"\"Kill Yuu...\"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"nameNarration":"Kuroe","narration":"The air is filled...","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"...with the scent of night jasmine and the sea."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"\"My story is already over.\"","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"\"Everyone is moving ahead to the future@without me.\""},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"nameNarration":"Kuroe","narration":"Who is this?@I can hear someone talking to me.","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"Her voice sounds a lot like Yuu-san's."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"\"So please...\"","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"\"Kill Yuu.\""},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"nameNarration":"Kuroe","narration":"You want me to...?","narrationEffect":"in"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"\"Before the passing days...\"","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"\"...erase everything she is...\""},{"narration":"\"Kill Yuu.\""},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"nameNarration":"Kuroe","narration":"This voice must belong @to someone precious that Yuu-san lost.","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"I don't know why, but that was the feeling I got.@It's the only thing I could think of."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"\"You know what I mean, don't you?\"","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"\"There's nothing after 'The End'...\""},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"nameNarration":"Kuroe","narration":"Yeah. I know.","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"The future is always lonely."},{"narration":"What's important, what's right—@those things only exist in the past."},{"narration":"Don't let my soul..."},{"narration":"...drift any further away from that girl..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bgm":"stop","narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeInTime":1.5}]},"version":3}
